title: #92Noon! Kyndra/Gleeman/Birk/Skaggs
description: MNUFC's Kyndra de St Aubin is in studio to kick off the show, followed by Gleeman in for an hour on the Twins and his cousin's wedding. You'll hear a two minute chat between PA & Mike Zimmer to start the final hour with Matt Birk in studio!
